382132,97,1162,2,33,1,247,23,"Tatrāyaṃ sabbakoṭṭhāsesu anupubbakathā– kesā tāva pakativaṇṇena kāḷakā addāriṭṭhakavaṇṇā, saṇṭhānato dīghavaṭṭalikā tulādaṇḍasaṇṭhānā, disato uparimadisāya jātā, okāsato ubhosu passesu kaṇṇacūḷikāhi, purato nalāṭantena, pacchato galavāṭakena paricchinnā. "
382133,97,1162,34,38,1,43,4,Sīsakaṭāhaveṭhanaṃ allacammaṃ kesānaṃ okāso. 
