383290,97,1355,2,38,1,332,23,"Apica ekādasa dhammā samādhisambojjhaṅgassa uppādāya saṃvattanti– vatthuvisadakiriyatā , indriyasamattapaṭipādanatā, nimittakusalatā, samaye cittassa paggaṇhanatā, samaye cittassa niggahaṇanatā, samaye sampahaṃsanatā, samaye ajjhupekkhaṇatā, asamāhitapuggalaparivajjanatā, samāhitapuggalasevanatā, jhānavimokkhapaccavekkhaṇatā, tadadhimuttatāti. "
383291,97,1355,39,46,1,84,7,Tattha vatthuvisadakiriyatā ca indriyasamattapaṭipādanatā ca vuttanayeneva veditabbā. 
383292,97,1356,2,6,1,54,4,Nimittakusalatā nāma kasiṇanimittassa uggahaṇakusalatā. 
383293,97,1356,7,24,1,167,14,"Samaye cittassa {paggahaṇanatā}ti yasmiṃ samaye atisithilavīriyatādīhi līnaṃ cittaṃ hoti, tasmiṃ samaye dhammavicayavīriyapītisambojjhaṅgasamuṭṭhāpanena tassa paggaṇhanaṃ. "
383294,97,1356,25,41,1,171,14,"Samaye cittassa {niggahaṇanatā}ti yasmiṃ samaye accāraddhavīriyatādīhi uddhaṭaṃ cittaṃ hoti, tasmiṃ samaye passaddhisamādhiupekkhāsambojjhaṅgasamuṭṭhāpanena tassa niggaṇhanaṃ. "
383295,97,1356,42,59,1,169,15,"Samaye {sampahaṃsanatā}ti yasmiṃ samaye cittaṃ paññāpayogamandatāya vā upasamasukhānadhigamena vā nirassādaṃ hoti, tasmiṃ samaye aṭṭhasaṃvegavatthupaccavekkhaṇena saṃvejeti. "
383296,97,1356,60,80,1,180,16,"Aṭṭha saṃvegavatthūni nāma jātijarābyādhimaraṇāni cattāri, apāyadukkhaṃ pañcamaṃ, atīte vaṭṭamūlakaṃ dukkhaṃ, anāgate vaṭṭamūlakaṃ dukkhaṃ, paccuppanne āhārapariyeṭṭhimūlakaṃ dukkhanti. "
383297,97,1356,81,85,1,44,4,Ratanattayaguṇānussaraṇena ca pasādaṃ janeti. 
383298,97,1356,86,90,1,36,4,Ayaṃ vuccati samaye sampahaṃsanatāti. 
383299,97,1357,2,27,1,245,24,"Samaye ajjhupekkhanatā nāma yasmiṃ samaye sammāpaṭipattiṃ āgamma alīnaṃ anuddhaṭaṃ anirassādaṃ ārammaṇe samappavattaṃ samathavīthipaṭipannaṃ cittaṃ hoti, tadāyaṃ paggahaniggahasampahaṃsanesu na byāpāraṃ āpajjati sārathī viya samappavattesu assesu. "
383300,97,1357,28,32,1,37,4,Ayaṃ vuccati samaye ajjhupekkhanatāti. 
