385603,97,1782,77,100,1,160,19,"Ye pana dhammā tamhā tamhā rūpārūpappabhedā hetuto jātā, tesaṃ atthabhāvaṃ, tassa tassa ca rūpārūpadhammappabhedassa hetuno dhammabhāvaṃ dassetuṃ‘ dhammavāro’ vutto. "
385604,97,1782,101,113,1,121,9,"Jarāmaraṇādīnaṃ pana atthabhāvaṃ, jarāmaraṇādisamudayasaṅkhātānaṃ jātiādīnañca dhammabhāvaṃ dassetuṃ‘ paccayākāravāro’ vutto. "
385605,97,1782,114,132,1,160,15,"Tato pariyattisaṅkhātassa tassa tassa bhāsitassa dhammabhāvaṃ, bhāsitasaṅkhātena paccayena pattabbassa bhāsitatthassa ca atthabhāvaṃ dassetuṃ‘ pariyattivāro’ vutto. "
385606,97,1783,2,16,1,130,13,"Tattha ca yasmā bhāsitaṃ ñatvā tassattho ñāyati, tasmā bhāsitabhāsitatthakkamena uppaṭipāṭiyā paṭhamaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā niddiṭṭhā. "
385607,97,1783,17,32,1,116,10,Pariyattidhammassa ca pabhedadassanatthaṃ‘‘ tattha katamā dhammapaṭisambhidā’’ ti pucchāpubbaṅgamo paṭiniddesavāro vutto. 
