385618,97,1786,60,77,1,161,15,"Vipākakiriyavāresu vipākakiriyānaṃ atthena saṅgahitattā, dhammapaṭisambhidaṃ chaḍḍetvā, ekekasmiṃ vipākacitte ca kiriyacitte ca tisso tissova paṭisambhidā vibhattā. "
