389443,98,201,24,40,1,124,13,Ayaṃ vuccati puggalo {samayavimutto}ti ettha aṭṭhasamāpattilābhī puthujjano tena nāmakāyena phusitvā viharatīti vattuṃ vaṭṭati. 
389444,98,201,41,52,1,46,7,Pāḷiyaṃ pana‘‘ ekacce āsavā parikkhīṇā’’ ti vuttaṃ. 
389445,98,201,53,64,1,59,10,"Puthujjanassa ca khīṇā āsavā nāma natthi, tasmā so na gahito. "
389446,98,201,65,73,1,82,8,Aṭṭhasamāpattilābhī khīṇāsavopi tena nāmakāyena phusitvā viharatīti vattuṃ vaṭṭati. 
389447,98,201,74,84,1,59,9,"Tassa pana aparikkhīṇāsavā nāma natthi, tasmā sopi na gahito. "
