389455,98,202,76,83,1,56,7,Maggavimokkhena vimuccanassa samayo vā asamayo vā natthi. 
389456,98,202,84,104,1,168,18,"Yassa saddhā balavatī, vipassanā ca āraddhā, tassa gacchantassa tiṭṭhantassa nisīdantassa nipajjantassa khādantassa bhuñjantassa maggaphalapaṭivedho nāma na hotīti natthi. "
389457,98,202,105,124,1,150,19,Iti maggavimokkhena vimuccanassa samayo vā asamayo vā natthīti heṭṭhā gahite ca aggahite ca saṅkaḍḍhitvā imaṃ piṭṭhivaṭṭakaṃ tantiṃ āropesi dhammarājā. 
