389460,98,203,2,15,1,93,8,"3. Kuppadhammākuppadhammaniddesesu– yassa adhigato samāpattidhammo kuppati nassati, so kuppadhammo. "
389461,98,203,16,21,1,59,5,Rūpasahagatānan ti rūpanimittasaṅkhātena rūpena sahagatānaṃ. 
