389981,98,281,28,33,1,59,4,"Tamojotiparāyaṇo pubbakārī, jotijotiparāyaṇo kataññukatavedī. "
389982,98,281,34,39,1,44,4,"Desetā pubbakārī, paṭipajjitā kataññukatavedī. "
389983,98,281,40,49,1,75,7,"Sadevake loke arahaṃ sammāsambuddho pubbakārī, ariyasāvako kataññukatavedīti. "
